No prob, Soulstice.

And Orchid, there are no windows in the CF.

::Kluster/Fliq/Grimmler/Killfest/Greven/EndBringer::

Kluster nods, glancing at Diskus. He had a feeling he should remember 
the bot, but he had no time for lengthy recollections right now.

"Of course you can join," he pauses as a scream passes through the 
area, but pays little attention to it for now, "We're about to start 
repairs on the ships, would you care to help?"

He taps a few buttons on his wrist comp, setting the shields of the 
CF to flicker off and allow any Maximals through when any approached.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Fliq arrives at the Cybertronian Fire, dragging Grimmler with him. He 
had waited till the battle was over to begin. Fliq walks into the CF, 
dragging Grimmler to the CR chambers.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Killfest turns around, looking around the battlefield and then 
sending a command to his team to go back to base. He watches Greven 
and EndBringer depart, and then flies off toward New Orleans.
